27
28typedef struct isc_ht_node isc_ht_node_t;
29
30#define ISC_HT_MAGIC ISC_MAGIC('H', 'T', 'a', 'b')
31#define ISC_HT_VALID(ht) ISC_MAGIC_VALID(ht, ISC_HT_MAGIC)
32
33struct isc_ht_node {
34 void *value;
35 isc_ht_node_t *next;
36 size_t keysize;
37 unsigned char key[FLEXIBLE_ARRAY_MEMBER];
38};
39
40struct isc_ht {
41 unsigned int magic;
42 isc_mem_t *mctx;
43 size_t size;
44 size_t mask;
45 unsigned int count;
46 isc_ht_node_t **table;
47};
48
49struct isc_ht_iter {
50 isc_ht_t *ht;
51 size_t i;
52 isc_ht_node_t *cur;
53};
54
55isc_result_t
56isc_ht_init(isc_ht_t **htp, isc_mem_t *mctx, uint8_t bits) {
57 isc_ht_t *ht = NULL;
58 size_t i;
59
60 REQUIRE(htp != NULL && *htp == NULL);
61 REQUIRE(mctx != NULL);
62 REQUIRE(bits >= 1 && bits <= (sizeof(size_t)*8 - 1));
63
64 ht = isc_mem_get(mctx, sizeof(struct isc_ht));
65 if (ht == NULL) {
66 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
67 }
68
69 ht->mctx = NULL;
70 isc_mem_attach(mctx, &ht->mctx);
71
72 ht->size = ((size_t)1<<bits);
73 ht->mask = ((size_t)1<<bits)-1;
74 ht->count = 0;
75
76 ht->table = isc_mem_get(ht->mctx, ht->size * sizeof(isc_ht_node_t*));
77 if (ht->table == NULL) {
78 isc_mem_putanddetach(&ht->mctx, ht, sizeof(struct isc_ht));
79 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
80 }
81
82 for (i = 0; i < ht->size; i++) {
83 ht->table[i] = NULL;
84 }
85
86 ht->magic = ISC_HT_MAGIC;
87
88 *htp = ht;
89 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
90}
91
92void
93isc_ht_destroy(isc_ht_t **htp) {
94 isc_ht_t *ht;
95 size_t i;
96
97 REQUIRE(htp != NULL);
98
99 ht = *htp;
100 REQUIRE(ISC_HT_VALID(ht));
101
102 ht->magic = 0;
103
104 for (i = 0; i < ht->size; i++) {
105 isc_ht_node_t *node = ht->table[i];
106 while (node != NULL) {
107 isc_ht_node_t *next = node->next;
108 ht->count--;
109 isc_mem_put(ht->mctx, node,
110 offsetof(isc_ht_node_t, key) +
111 node->keysize);
112 node = next;
113 }
114 }
115
116 INSIST(ht->count == 0);
117
118 isc_mem_put(ht->mctx, ht->table, ht->size * sizeof(isc_ht_node_t*));
119 isc_mem_putanddetach(&ht->mctx, ht, sizeof(struct isc_ht));
120
121 *htp = NULL;
122}
123
124isc_result_t
125isc_ht_add(isc_ht_t *ht, const unsigned char *key,
126 uint32_t keysize, void *value)
127{
128 isc_ht_node_t *node;
129 uint32_t hash;
130
131 REQUIRE(ISC_HT_VALID(ht));
132 REQUIRE(key != NULL && keysize > 0);
133
134 hash = isc_hash_function(key, keysize, true, NULL);
135 node = ht->table[hash & ht->mask];
136 while (node != NULL) {
137 if (keysize == node->keysize &&
138 memcmp(key, node->key, keysize) == 0) {
139 return (ISC_R_EXISTS);
140 }
141 node = node->next;
142 }
143
144 node = isc_mem_get(ht->mctx, offsetof(isc_ht_node_t, key) + keysize);
145 if (node == NULL)
146 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
147
148 memmove(node->key, key, keysize);
149 node->keysize = keysize;
150 node->next = ht->table[hash & ht->mask];
151 node->value = value;
152
153 ht->count++;
154 ht->table[hash & ht->mask] = node;
155 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
156}
157
158isc_result_t
159isc_ht_find(const isc_ht_t *ht, const unsigned char *key,
160 uint32_t keysize, void **valuep)
161{
162 isc_ht_node_t *node;
163 uint32_t hash;
164
165 REQUIRE(ISC_HT_VALID(ht));
166 REQUIRE(key != NULL && keysize > 0);
167 REQUIRE(valuep == NULL || *valuep == NULL);
168
169 hash = isc_hash_function(key, keysize, true, NULL);
170 node = ht->table[hash & ht->mask];
171 while (node != NULL) {
172 if (keysize == node->keysize &&
173 memcmp(key, node->key, keysize) == 0)
174 {
175 if (valuep != NULL)
176 *valuep = node->value;
177 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
178 }
179 node = node->next;
180 }
181
182 return (ISC_R_NOTFOUND);
183}
184
185isc_result_t
186isc_ht_delete(isc_ht_t *ht, const unsigned char *key, uint32_t keysize) {
187 isc_ht_node_t *node, *prev;
188 uint32_t hash;
189
190 REQUIRE(ISC_HT_VALID(ht));
191 REQUIRE(key != NULL && keysize > 0);
192
193 prev = NULL;
194 hash = isc_hash_function(key, keysize, true, NULL);
195 node = ht->table[hash & ht->mask];
196 while (node != NULL) {
197 if (keysize == node->keysize &&
198 memcmp(key, node->key, keysize) == 0) {
199 if (prev == NULL)
200 ht->table[hash & ht->mask] = node->next;
201 else
202 prev->next = node->next;
203 isc_mem_put(ht->mctx, node,
204 offsetof(isc_ht_node_t, key) +
205 node->keysize);
206 ht->count--;
207
208 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
209 }
210
211 prev = node;
212 node = node->next;
213 }
214 return (ISC_R_NOTFOUND);
215}
216
217isc_result_t
218isc_ht_iter_create(isc_ht_t *ht, isc_ht_iter_t **itp) {
219 isc_ht_iter_t *it;
220
221 REQUIRE(ISC_HT_VALID(ht));
222 REQUIRE(itp != NULL && *itp == NULL);
223
224 it = isc_mem_get(ht->mctx, sizeof(isc_ht_iter_t));
225 if (it == NULL)
226 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
227
228 it->ht = ht;
229 it->i = 0;
230 it->cur = NULL;
231
232 *itp = it;
233
234 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
235}
236
237void
238isc_ht_iter_destroy(isc_ht_iter_t **itp) {
239 isc_ht_iter_t *it;
240 isc_ht_t *ht;
241
242 REQUIRE(itp != NULL && *itp != NULL);
243
244 it = *itp;
245 ht = it->ht;
246 isc_mem_put(ht->mctx, it, sizeof(isc_ht_iter_t));
247
248 *itp = NULL;
249}
250
251isc_result_t
252isc_ht_iter_first(isc_ht_iter_t *it) {
253 REQUIRE(it != NULL);
254
255 it->i = 0;
256 while (it->i < it->ht->size && it->ht->table[it->i] == NULL)
257 it->i++;
258
259 if (it->i == it->ht->size)
260 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
261
262 it->cur = it->ht->table[it->i];
263
264 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
265}
266
267isc_result_t
268isc_ht_iter_next(isc_ht_iter_t *it) {
269 REQUIRE(it != NULL);
270 REQUIRE(it->cur != NULL);
271
272 it->cur = it->cur->next;
273 if (it->cur == NULL) {
274 do {
275 it->i++;
276 } while (it->i < it->ht->size && it->ht->table[it->i] == NULL);
277 if (it->i >= it->ht->size)
278 return (ISC_R_NOMORE);
279 it->cur = it->ht->table[it->i];
280 }
281
282 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
283}
284
285isc_result_t
286isc_ht_iter_delcurrent_next(isc_ht_iter_t *it) {
287 isc_result_t result = ISC_R_SUCCESS;
288 isc_ht_node_t *to_delete = NULL;
289 isc_ht_node_t *prev = NULL;
290 isc_ht_node_t *node = NULL;
291 uint32_t hash;
292 isc_ht_t *ht;
293 REQUIRE(it != NULL);
294 REQUIRE(it->cur != NULL);
295 to_delete = it->cur;
296 ht = it->ht;
297
298 it->cur = it->cur->next;
299 if (it->cur == NULL) {
300 do {
301 it->i++;
302 } while (it->i < ht->size && ht->table[it->i] == NULL);
303 if (it->i >= ht->size)
304 result = ISC_R_NOMORE;
305 else
306 it->cur = ht->table[it->i];
307 }
308
309 hash = isc_hash_function(to_delete->key, to_delete->keysize, true,
310 NULL);
311 node = ht->table[hash & ht->mask];
312 while (node != to_delete) {
313 prev = node;
314 node = node->next;
315 INSIST(node != NULL);
316 }
317
318 if (prev == NULL)
319 ht->table[hash & ht->mask] = node->next;
320 else
321 prev->next = node->next;
322 isc_mem_put(ht->mctx, node,
323 offsetof(isc_ht_node_t, key) + node->keysize);
324 ht->count--;
325
326 return (result);
327}
328
329void
330isc_ht_iter_current(isc_ht_iter_t *it, void **valuep) {
331 REQUIRE(it != NULL);
332 REQUIRE(it->cur != NULL);
333 REQUIRE(valuep != NULL && *valuep == NULL);
334
335 *valuep = it->cur->value;
336}
337
338void
339isc_ht_iter_currentkey(isc_ht_iter_t *it, unsigned char **key, size_t *keysize)
340{
341 REQUIRE(it != NULL);
342 REQUIRE(it->cur != NULL);
343 REQUIRE(key != NULL && *key == NULL);
344
345 *key = it->cur->key;
346 *keysize = it->cur->keysize;
347}

349unsigned int
350isc_ht_count(isc_ht_t *ht) {
351 REQUIRE(ISC_HT_VALID(ht));
352
353 return(ht->count);
354}
